{"tid":1525518,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「年輕人」不要被仇恨支配，入了身和心","createTime":"2019-09-01T01:10:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T17:13:40.000Z","uid":284195,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"46b412eea5108fde1c77d60192dfde93df6ac23a","tid":1525518,"uid":284195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:10:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">經過慢慢長夜，香港過了沉痛一夜<br />\n希望大家可以停一停想一想<br />\n耍冷靜思考不要被仇恨支配<br />\n因為仇恨會種<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><div style=\"text-align: left;\"></div></div>在你心<br />\n<br />\n看見一個個年輕人受傷很心痛，被打了，其實是入心的痛，每次希望你們快點回家，整晚沒有睡過<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n劉進圖訪問<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8KbGa_nl4GE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8KbGa_nl4GE&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b0ZHjOsADYkIOf4eYSwfwZo%3D&h=8809daf4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8KbGa_nl4GE</a><br />\n<br />\n現在籃絲被鼔吹仇曱甴，近日仇黑記<br />\n示威者被鼓吹仇警<br />\n年輕人可能你覺得自己有思考分柝，<br />\n但有風向，有臥底，有鬼，有監控<br />\n<br />\n這就係人鬥人，鬼打鬼，而且越見加烈<br />\n8.30 警察相信同袍被斬,之後增加示威者仇恨<br />\n8.31 same loop 示威者站內被打增加對 警察仇恨<br />\n無限loop............<br />\n<br />\n希望以站在對方視覺去睇件事，大家想想可以點去溝通協商，因為暴力只會增加暴力.<br />\n要甘多年輕人受傷很心痛，雖然冇大台但希望大家思考下不要作無謂犧牲這政府不配.<br />\n以武力解決問題是政府樂見，但大家香港人市民一定希望peacefully settle ，不想孩子被打<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Y2Y4pc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Y2Y4pc.jpg&h=d9462176&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n文化大革命自己 look <br />\n<br />\n有缐特輯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ggHrHQxt9u0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FggHrHQxt9u0&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b0ZHjOsADYkIOf4eYSwfwZo%3D&h=4067ec37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ggHrHQxt9u0</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n蘋果<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lDwGUOpi_mQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlDwGUOpi_mQ&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b0ZHjOsADYkIOf4eYSwfwZo%3D&h=8db23ef4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lDwGUOpi_mQ</a>"},{"pid":"e64121b0d23e9135d50bca5fded18116127453a1","tid":1525518,"uid":242083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:10:54.000Z","msg":"831恐襲同721恐襲冇分別<br />\n我正式宣佈香港警察係有牌黑社會兼恐怖分子<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/eYzNsiOy00o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FeYzNsiOy00o&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b0ZHjOsADYkIOf4eYSwfwZo%3D&h=07942aad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/eYzNsiOy00o</a>"},{"pid":"cceb4e9f510dd74883d22b96f64e926b2e1d1531","tid":1525518,"uid":284195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:11:49.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"096d7f801a15560c2433917ffba8234511ebbee0","tid":1525518,"uid":284195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:12:01.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"d6f03648811722b23d2d6617843bd5a75478cdf7","tid":1525518,"uid":284195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:12:12.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"a7a9457525f646982cca0d62e879a370a7b475a1","tid":1525518,"uid":284195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:12:26.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"73279e11e9c47820a7eb2d65f6ca7d75997ad4ad","tid":1525518,"uid":284195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:12:44.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"c98dbf8d0b0f7ea5db1a2a26b5a30ac856077e1a","tid":1525518,"uid":284195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:15:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />sad 廢中"},{"pid":"a0bb75b8a8b2d48901bcd7059187895b7412ec73","tid":1525518,"uid":284195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:23:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2e3b9dd5ff0989619ecd052e7ff2d7e676e96695","tid":1525518,"uid":124292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-